 Nigeria’s very own queen of Afro-pop, Tiwa Savage showed the love she has for her fans by staging a mini-concert at the Obalende Bus Park in Lagos today and it was such an amazing experience. The music goddess, who just released her brand new single “49-99“, was all shades of energetic as she thrilled the crowd with her hit songs, and when it was time for “49-99”, the whole place went up in flames as the crowd wanted more. Watch her performance below:   It's a totally shut down at the Obalende bridge as @tiwasavage gave us a thrilling performance #mediaroomhub #4999 A post shared by  Media Room Hub (@mediaroomhub_) on Sep 17, 2019 at 12:23pm PDT //www.instagram.com/embed.js The post Tiwa Savage Premieres “49-99” with an Energetic Performance at Obalende Bus Park, Lago | Watch appeared first on BellaNaija – Showcasing Africa to the world. Read today!. Source: Bella Naija